Synthesis of CQDs@ZIF-8@ZIF-8 (CQDs@ZIF-8
2
): The as-synthesized CQDs@ZIF-8 was redispersed into 20 mL methanol solution containing 30 mM 2-methylimidazole, and then 20 mL of Zn(NO3)2·6H2O methanol solution (30 mM) was added. Then let set the mixture for 1 h, and the formed CQDs@ZIF-8 2 was collected by centrifugation at 6000 rpm for 10 min. The white solid powder was washed with methanol several times and dried in an over at 50 °C for 6 h.

Synthesis of RhB@ZIF-8@ZIF-8 (RhB@ZIF-8

   2

): The as-prepared RhB@ZIF-8 was redispersed into 20 mL methanol solution containing 30 mM 2-methylimidazole, and then 20 mL of Zn(NO3)2·6H2O methanol solution (30 mM) was added. Then let set the mixture for 1 h, and the formed RhB@ZIF-82 was collected by centrifugation at 6000 rpm for 10 min. The pink solid powder was washed with methanol several times and dried in an over at 50 °C for 6 h.

Synthesis of CQDs@ZIF-8

   2

@RhB@ZIF-8: An as-synthesized CQDs@ZIF-82 composite was added into 14.0 mL of an aqueous solution of 0.41 mM CTAB and 790 mM 2-methylimidazole. The mixture was stirred for 10 min, and followed by the addition of 10 mL Zn(NO3)2·6H2O aqueous solution (97.5 mM). After stirring for a few seconds, different amounts (120, 200, and 240 μL) of 5 mM RhB aqueous solution was dropped, and the mixture continued to stir for 2 min, then let set the mixture for 1 h at room temperature. The resulting CQDs@ZIF-82@RhB@ZIF-8 were collected by centrifugation at 4000 rpm for 10 min and wash with methanol several times until no absorption peak of RhB molecule was detected in the replaced methanol solution. The light pink solid product was dried at 50 °C for 6 h.
